'''Freespan Starlanes Transport''' was a major starline that was in operation during the [[Separatist Crisis/Legends|Separatist Crisis]]. In [[23 BBY/Legends|23 BBY]], Freespan announced plans to double the number of scheduled liner departures for [[Ando/Legends|Ando]], following the planet's secession from the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]]. Freespan predicted increased travel from Andoan expatriates wishing to return. Other major starlines, such as [[Romodi Interstellar]] and [[Galaxy Tours/Legends|Galaxy Tours]], were thought to be following Freespan's lead and were set to announce similar increases.

